   sequel to the 2007 film Shootout at      
   Lokhandwala, and is based on the book    
   Dongri to Dubai.The film will dramatize  
   the first-ever registered encounter by   
   Mumbai police, where gangster Manya Surve
   was shot dead, which took place at the   
   junction next to Dr. Ambedkar college,   
   Wadala, Mumbai on 11 January 1982.
